{"tid":387977,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"請教有無基礎投資堂可以上？","createTime":"2017-09-05T05:55:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-07T19:27:21.000Z","uid":140829,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b2c56e8707e49ce41c70b078893e804c00326d9c","tid":387977,"uid":140829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T05:55:12.000Z","msg":"人大左先突然想學，但從唔相信朋友講話買返隻就學到架啦，聽多d就得呢d說話，因為咁既方法太散漫，而我直情係返part time有時間出去上下堂果隻，所以想係度請教大家有無d咩堂係學到基礎野，概念，思考模式之類；老老豆豆真係唔想要求number果d堂，學到我自己去尋找我死我事，但基本野都唔曉講咩都覺得哂氣<br />\n<br />\n另外有朋友介紹我上《我要做股神》果個初學+入門班，請問有無巴打絲打有經驗？<br />\n<br />\n🙇🏻🙇🏻🙇🏻🙇🏻🙇🏻🙇🏻真心求教，謝謝"},{"pid":"e5f846771155575cb8749757ddbcf81f05540af7","tid":387977,"uid":18886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T05:59:29.000Z","msg":"自己睇書比較實際<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da7d818269fc2510b8483bb8bca7c4eed0043264","tid":387977,"uid":55296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T06:00:38.000Z","msg":"有自己睇書，但睇完書同買係兩回事<br />\n睇完窮爸爸富爸爸，但依然唔識買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfd7ba670668c9ca2a90b3d4d5e5f149041156d0","tid":387977,"uid":18886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T06:15:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有自己睇書，但睇完書同買係兩回事<br />\n睇完窮爸爸富爸爸，但依然唔識買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n窮爸爸富爸爸都唔係教人點揀股票既書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係教人不斷去購買有價值資產去增加被動收入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a62700bb4f301d3e9b324cd478fc0fbb72c7025","tid":387977,"uid":70367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T06:18:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有自己睇書，但睇完書同買係兩回事<br />\n睇完窮爸爸富爸爸，但依然唔識買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=